# Project artifacts
# data/ runtime output is ignored, EXCEPT:
#   - data/graphs/ : pre-extracted computation graph pkls
#   - data/raw/    : Modal / PSC profiling CSVs (small text, shared for team review)
data/*
!data/graphs/
!data/graphs/**
!data/raw/
!data/raw/**
datasets/
*.csv
*.parquet
*.jsonl
checkpoints/
runs/
logs/
wandb/
outputs/
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt
*.onnx
*.safetensors

# Re-include data/ subdirs after the broad per-extension excludes above.
# (git evaluates rules top-to-bottom; later rules override earlier ones.)
!data/raw/*.csv
!data/raw/**/*.csv          # decode-mode CSVs live in data/raw/decode/
!data/graphs/*.pkl

# Misc
*.log
.env.local
